
;<Program title>

jmp start

;data


;code
start: nop
MVI A,00H
LXI H,2100H
LOOP1: PUSH PSW
PUSH H
CALL DISPLAY
CALL DELAY
POP H
POP PSW
INX H
INR A
CPI 1DH
JNZ LOOP1
JMP END
DISPLAY: RET
DELAY: MVI C,015H
LABEL1: MVI B,0FFH
LABEL2: MVI A,03FH
LABEL3: DCR A
JNZ LABEL3
DCR B
JNZ LABEL2
DCR C
JNZ LABEL1
RET
END: HLT